{"tid":1799920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海璇「鳳凰樓」4房大戶1.53億沽    呎價首破7萬大關創新高","createTime":"2019-12-27T10:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T11:06:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea0d811798c2b14409df51e0dd58720c81ef08f0","tid":1799920,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191227/large/1577433541_d2b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191227%2Flarge%2F1577433541_d2b5.jpg&h=1381955d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海璇管理費每呎5.98元<br />\n<br />\n新地(016)趕2019年完結前推售天水圍新盤Wetland Seasons Park之際，旗下北角豪宅海璇，透過招標出售1伙4房大戶，造價達1.53億元，呎價7.34萬元，銀碼及呎價均下項目新高紀錄，呎價同打破港島東最貴呎價成交。<br />\n<br />\n按一手住宅成交紀錄顯示，招標售出單位為海璇第1B期1座17樓A室，實用面積2,083方呎，另設有456方呎平台，單位屬4房連兩個套房，成交價1.53億元，實用呎價首次突破7萬元大關，呎價73,469元。單位為頂層對下單位，屬俗稱「鳳凰樓」。"},{"pid":"dca017c2c32877e3176a53739040727a934dc92d","tid":1799920,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:31:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"240d31d715356d6a29301c9b5ebb19f9f1eeacc0","tid":1799920,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T10:37:27.000Z","msg":"1.5億喺福建買層2千幾呎嘅樓 有幾弱智先會咁做?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06cc7553521fa55dabd1be6d33e0f3be41ab63e","tid":1799920,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T11:06:17.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/